column5: Feb 13th Dunnville Ice Report.... Ice is in great shape 5 to 6" all places checked last night ..only one spot i seen thats not safe ..and thats on the  far side of the river ...if this keeps up ill be out on the snow moblie later today checking some spots i haven't tried this winter ...
A few pictures of what the ice looked like on the river 2 days ago..
Ice looks good Steve, thanks. Just haven't made it down your way yet, gonna hafta soon.
Your not gonna catch too many fish if ya pee in your hole's Fishmaster... Thanks for the report
Keeps it from freezing   and fish like salted minnows
Derby is next Saturday JM...be nice to see ya for a ice tourney ..
